v: 9
t: Takheun lon rasul kon ureueng baro Dileekon sit le dum rasul Allah Peue nyang geupeugot keu lon ngon gata c Di lon pih hana lon teuʻoh peugah Di lon lonikot peue nyang Neuwahi Bak lon Neuyue bri peue nyang peurintah Di lon nyoe mantong Neuyue peuingat Meunan nyata that nyang Neuyue peugah